flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Process: Mulai Round 1 MAD]
    B --> C[Process: Agen Menghasilkan Stance + Confidence]
    C --> D{Decision: Konsensus Tercapai?}
    D -->|Ya| E[Process: Early Termination]
    E --> F[Process: Aggregasi Voting]
    D -->|Tidak| G{Decision: Round < Max Rounds?}
    G -->|Ya| H[Process: Deliberasi Round Berikutnya]
    H --> C
    G -->|Tidak| I[Process: Stop karena Max Rounds]
    I --> F
    F --> J[/Output: Keputusan Akhir/]
    J --> K([End])
